column4: Chkhorotsku Municipality is the self-governing unit, located in the Samegrelo-Zemo Svaneti region.
column5: Chkhorotsku Municipality consists of 13 administrative-territorial units: 1 town - Chkhorotsku, 13 village unions - Sabume, Mukhuri, Lesichine, Lower Chkhorotsku, Virtshkhi, Akhuti, Chogi, Napichkhovo, Lentsurtsumi, Nakiani. And 2 separate villages - Taia, Zumi.
column7: Population according to gender: female - 15,328; male - 14,115
column8: Population according to residence: urban - 4,916; rural - 24,527
column9: Population according to ethnicity: Georgian - 29,895; Russian - 127; Abkhaz - 36; Ukrainian - 20; Ossetian - 2; Armenian - 30; Azeri - 1; Greek - 1
